  "prompt": "What are the most interesting products and innovations that Aqua America is coming out with in 2016?",
  "response": "In 2016, Aqua America, a major water utility company, focused on delivering safe and reliable water and wastewater services rather than developing consumer-facing products or innovations. However, the company may have been involved in several initiatives and improvements around that time, such as:\n\n1. **Infrastructure Investments**: Aqua America typically invests in upgrading and maintaining its water and wastewater infrastructure. This can include replacing old pipes, upgrading treatment plants, and enhancing system efficiency and reliability.\n\n2. **Sustainability Efforts**: The company often undertakes projects to improve environmental sustainability. This might involve reducing water loss through advanced leak detection technologies or improving energy efficiency in their operations.\n\n3. **Customer Service Enhancements**: Aqua America might also focus on improving customer service through enhanced billing systems, customer portals, and communication platforms to provide better service and support to their customers.\n\n4. **Acquisitions and Expansions**: The company has historically grown through acquiring smaller water systems. Such strategic acquisitions can allow them to expand their service areas and improve water services in new regions.\n\nThese areas of focus are typical for utility companies like Aqua America as they strive to provide high-quality service and ensure long-term water sustainability and reliability for their customers.",
